OL,4,Ctracks jailed for life for attempted
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FA man who pushed a stranger onto the
OL,8,Ftracks of the London Underground has
OL,9,Fbeen jailed for life with a minimum
OL,10,Fterm of eight years.
OL,12,FBrwa Shorsh, 24, was sentenced on
OL,13,FThursday at Inner London Crown Court
OL,14,Fafter he was found guilty of attempted
OL,15,Fmurder, the CPS said.
OL,17,FOn February 3, Shorsh, of no fixed
OL,18,Faddress, pushed postman Tadeusz
OL,19,FPotoczek off a platform at Oxford
OL,20,FCircus station and into the path of an
OL,21,Foncoming Victoria Line train.
