OL,7,FMr Potoczek, who was 60 at the time of
OL,8,Fthe attack, was on his way home from
OL,9,Fwork and had walked past Shorsh who
OL,10,Fwas sitting on a bench.
OL,12,FWithout any provocation, Shorsh leapt
OL,13,Fup and shoved him off the platform and
OL,14,Fonto the train tracks, the CPS said.
OL,16,FThe victim managed to stay on his feet
OL,17,Fand a passerby helped him to climb
OL,18,Fback up onto the platform just as a
OL,19,Ftrain pulled into the station.
