OL,7,FA jury heard that Mr Potoczek narrowly
OL,8,Fmissed touching the live rail on the
OL,9,Fsouthbound Victoria Line.
OL,11,FThe driver of an oncoming train said
OL,12,F"if he had been on the track a few
OL,13,Fseconds later, he would have been
OL,14,Fkilled", Inner London Crown Court
OL,15,Fheard.
OL,17,FMr Justice Kelleher awarded the
OL,18,Fpasserby who aided Mr Potoczek #1,000
OL,19,Fafter commending his bravery and quick
OL,20,Freaction, the CPS said.
