OL,7,FKurdish migrant Shorsh, who had been
OL,8,Fsleeping rough in England since 2020,
OL,9,Fran off before the police arrived and
OL,10,Fwas arrested later that day.
OL,12,FHe admitted during his police
OL,13,Finterview that he had pushed the
OL,14,Fvictim onto the track because "he had
OL,15,Fgiven him a dirty look" which made him
OL,16,Fangry, the CPS said.
