OL,7,FMaxine Jarrousse-Jones, a senior crown
OL,8,Fprosecutor at the CPS, said: "Brwa
OL,9,FShorsh attempted to kill the victim by
OL,10,Fdeliberately and forcefully pushing
OL,11,Fhim into the path of an approaching
OL,12,Ftrain.
OL,14,F"He intended to harm the victim and it
OL,15,Fis impossible to imagine anything that
OL,16,Fcould ever justify pushing anyone in
OL,17,Ffront of a train like that.
