OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,F"If not for the victim's quick-
OL,8,Fthinking, the courage of the other
OL,9,Fpassenger who came to his rescue and
OL,10,Fthe speed at which the train driver
OL,11,Fbrought the train to a halt, Shorsh's
OL,12,Factions could have cost the victim his
OL,13,Flife.
OL,15,F"Commuters should be able to travel
OL,16,Ffreely without fear of violence or
OL,17,Fharm and I hope this sentencing is a
OL,18,Freminder that such acts will not be
OL,19,Ftolerated and will be prosecuted as
OL,20,Ffully as the law allows."
